text_block_list.name: Little Cocon
text_block_list.text: … Wow. I didn't know you guys were here for the finals.

text_block_list.name: Bitter Glasse
text_block_list.text: Thanks for the Aoharu Hai! I had a great race thanks to you guys.

text_block_list.name: Little Cocon
text_block_list.text: … Well, but that's that. It has nothing to do with today's race.

text_block_list.name: Little Cocon
text_block_list.text: Our team will win this time. Don't forget that.

text_block_list.name: Little Cocon
text_block_list.text: … Oh shut up. I just mixed them up.
